					"type": 23,
					"value": "Ceremony of Gortash becoming the Grand Duke.\r\nThe start of the dialog depends on whether Steel Watchers are enabled (present) or not.\r\nIn the dialog Gortash tells you to kill Orin and then concludes the ceremony. Player can attack but it would be very hard to win."
